{
  "name": "GetSecret",
  "description": "Retrieve a Secret",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "id": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Unique identifier of Secret to manage"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "id"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "http://microcks.local/secrets/{id}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "A Secret allows grouping informations on how to access a restricted resource such as a repsoitory URL. Secrets are typically used by ImpoortJobs.",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**caCertPem**",
            "**description**: Description of this Secret",
            "**id**: Unique identifier of Secret",
            "**name**: Unique distinct name of Secret",
            "**password**",
            "**token**",
            "**tokenHeader**",
            "**username**"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
